  CALL FOR PAPERSMarch 24-26, 2020 Osaka, JapanConference Theme: Sustainable EnergyAnnual Conference on Engineering and Information Technology aims to provide the best platform for researchers, engineers, as well as industrial professionals to present their research results and discuss the future and development in engineering, information technology and related fields With members from around the world focusing on Sustainable Energy, this will be the best opportunity for the worlds scholars and professionals to discuss the urgent energy issues, including energy efficiency, energy engineering, sustainable development, alternative energy and beyond.We sincerely invite you to join us. Please notice that full research paper or abstracts are welcome and kindly submit your paper through our official website.Tracks:- Sustainable Energy (Special Session)- Biological Engineering- Chemical Engineering- Civil Engineering- Computer and Information Sciences- Electrical and Electronic Engineering- Environmental SciencesSubmit NowImportant DatesSubmission Deadline: December 5, 2019Registration & Payment Deadline:January 22, 2020Need any assistances, please contact: aceait@aceait.orgFor more information, please visit our website: http://www.aceait.org  

